member.summary:
Load audio for playback from a file.
This is equivalent to calling: Mixer.LoadAudioIO(mixer, SDL.IOFromFile(path, "rb"), predecode, true);
This function loads data from a path on the filesystem. There is also a version that loads from an SDL_IOStream (), and one that accepts properties for ultimate control ().

